---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Getting started">
  <article class="doc">
    <div class="eyebrow">Docs / 01</div>
    <h1>Getting started</h1>
    <p class="intro">Build the native lawlint binary, point it at a document, and get a focused list of things worth revising.</p>
    <h2>Build the CLI</h2>
    <pre>git clone https://github.com/sethtjf/lawlint
cd lawlint
cargo build --release -p lawlint-cli</pre>
    <p>One-line installers and a download page are coming in the next release.</p>
    <h2>Run the CLI</h2>
    <pre>./target/release/lawlint contract.md
cat memo.txt | ./target/release/lawlint - --format json</pre>
    <p>Markdown files automatically skip fenced code blocks. For piped Markdown, add <code>--markdown</code>.</p>
    <h2>Exit codes</h2>
    <ul><li><code>0</code> when no errors are found and the warning limit is not exceeded.</li><li><code>1</code> when an error is found or <code>--max-warnings</code> is exceeded.</li></ul>
    <p><a href="/docs/cli">Next: CLI reference →</a></p>
  </article>
</Layout>
